Class ConstraintSolver.ConstraintSolverData

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    ConstraintSolver

    public static class ConstraintSolver.ConstraintSolverData
extends Object
    This structure contains data from the constraint solver that is used to solve each joint constraint.
